      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ELLA KNOWS (3) flew the lids from the middle with a slick turn of foot before finishing second (22.79) and beaten 6 lengths over 400m at this track. Good beginner aided by a nice draw. Can measure up this time. WHISKY BENT (8) goes very well at this journey here having never missed the frame including two wins and three placings. Placed last time (22.97) at this track in a Grade 5, finishing second and beaten 0.8 lengths. Can hit the frame with the right run. JONESY REVENGE (1) finished fifth last time at Maitland but could not have been more impressive before that in his strong 18.20 win at Richmond over 320m. Top win two back and can measure up again. SHY HI (2) is worth some thought after placing last start.",
